item.title: SoftLayer_Network_SecurityGroup_OrderBinding
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_SecurityGroup_OrderBinding Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_SecurityGroup_OrderBinding data type contains links between security groups and product orders. Local guestId The ID of the Virtual Guest associated with the security group. Type: integer id The unique ID for a security group, order, binding Type: integer orderId The ID of the order associated with the security group. Type: integer securityGroupId The ID of the security group that is associated with the order.
